params.markdown: This dataset **requires access** to the Kubernetes scheduler endpoint. Refer [here](https://docs.elastic.co/en/integrations/kubernetes#scheduler-and-controllermanager) to learn how to enable it. In some "As a Service" Kubernetes implementations, like GKE or AKS, it is **not possible** to access its metrics.
